Package com.iver.cit.javacad.util

Class Summary
AcadColor This class allows to convert Autocad colors in Java colors
AcadExtrusionCalculator This class allows to apply the extrusion transformation of Autocad given by an array of doubles to a point given by an array of doubles too.
ArcFromBulgeCalculator This class calculates an arc given by a start and end points and a bulge
GisModelCurveCalculator This class allows to obtain arcs and circles given by the most usual parameters, in a Gis geometry model.
TextToUnicodeConverter This class allows to convert an Autocad text in an Unicode text
